631
00:24:38,480 --> 00:24:39,599
Go, then!

632
00:24:40,079 --> 00:24:42,079
Walk out, and do not come back!

633
00:25:04,279 --> 00:25:04,799
Ming.

634
00:25:06,200 --> 00:25:07,680
Let's have lunch today.

635
00:25:09,160 --> 00:25:10,240
Meet me at Tong's Noodle Shop.

636
00:25:11,510 --> 00:25:13,990
(Tong's Noodle Shop)

637
00:25:23,920 --> 00:25:24,640
Stop waiting.

638
00:25:24,920 --> 00:25:26,559
I have served this three times.

639
00:25:27,119 --> 00:25:28,960
If you pass out from low blood sugar,

640
00:25:29,000 --> 00:25:30,279
I will have to call an ambulance.

641
00:25:32,480 --> 00:25:33,519
I will get you a new one.

642
00:25:35,400 --> 00:25:36,759
The kids have their own lives.

643
00:25:36,960 --> 00:25:38,680
Maybe they are busy right now.

644
00:25:51,039 --> 00:25:52,039
Here is what I think.

645
00:25:52,799 --> 00:25:55,079
The money in the wall

646
00:25:56,119 --> 00:25:56,920
belongs to Hu Deshuai.

647
00:25:58,839 --> 00:25:59,920
And the money underground

648
00:26:00,960 --> 00:26:02,680
was buried

649
00:26:02,799 --> 00:26:03,559
by Chen Zinuo's father.

650
00:26:05,799 --> 00:26:07,000
Stop sighing like that.

651
00:26:07,000 --> 00:26:08,000
It is bad for your luck.

652
00:26:08,200 --> 00:26:09,480
What should I do with this anger?

653
00:26:09,480 --> 00:26:10,319
Where else can I let it out?

654
00:26:10,319 --> 00:26:11,119
Of course I have to sigh.

655
00:26:11,240 --> 00:26:13,720
You can let it out

656
00:26:13,720 --> 00:26:14,720
some other way.

657
00:26:14,720 --> 00:26:16,160
Just sing it out.

658
00:26:16,799 --> 00:26:17,200
Hoo.

659
00:26:17,519 --> 00:26:18,079
Hoo-ha.

660
00:26:18,599 --> 00:26:19,160
Anything works.

661
00:26:20,920 --> 00:26:21,960
That actually sounds nice.

662
00:26:25,720 --> 00:26:26,920
Let's check the messages.

663
00:26:35,759 --> 00:26:36,960
Good heavens.

664
00:26:38,720 --> 00:26:39,319
Wen Yitong.

665
00:26:39,799 --> 00:26:41,160
Was it fun making fools of us?

666
00:26:41,400 --> 00:26:42,400
Looking down on everyone

667
00:26:42,400 --> 00:26:43,119
felt good, did it?

668
00:26:43,119 --> 00:26:43,880
What happened?

669
00:26:43,880 --> 00:26:44,880
Who leaked this?

670
00:26:44,880 --> 00:26:46,160
I always thought

671
00:26:46,200 --> 00:26:47,119
