672
00:26:47,200 --> 00:26:47,839
Beats me.

673
00:26:47,839 --> 00:26:48,920
I guess marriage changes people.

674
00:26:48,920 --> 00:26:49,400
Ming.

675
00:26:49,599 --> 00:26:50,559
Don't think

676
00:26:50,559 --> 00:26:51,279
turning off your phones

677
00:26:51,279 --> 00:26:52,079
and hiding from us

678
00:26:52,079 --> 00:26:53,240
