679
00:26:53,640 --> 00:26:55,039
After all that soup I made for you?

680
00:26:55,880 --> 00:26:57,599
Pick up. Why not picking up?

681
00:26:58,359 --> 00:26:58,880
Wen Yitong.

682
00:26:59,400 --> 00:27:00,759
You never won the lottery at all.

683
00:27:01,000 --> 00:27:02,079
I know it!

684
00:27:02,119 --> 00:27:02,559
Yu Ming.

685
00:27:02,559 --> 00:27:03,200
No wonder you have been

686
00:27:03,200 --> 00:27:03,960
