711
00:28:04,160 --> 00:28:05,079
She was fierce.

712
00:28:05,319 --> 00:28:06,799
A warrior woman.

713
00:28:06,839 --> 00:28:08,160
Her tongue was sharp as a blade.

714
00:28:08,680 --> 00:28:09,240
Yitong,

715
00:28:09,359 --> 00:28:11,119
