726
00:28:25,240 --> 00:28:25,759
Wenwen.

727
00:28:26,079 --> 00:28:26,799
Have you eaten?

728
00:28:27,000 --> 00:28:27,680
There is still food.

729
00:28:27,799 --> 00:28:28,480
I will heat it up for you.

730
00:28:28,559 --> 00:28:29,240
It will be ready soon.

731
00:28:29,519 --> 00:28:30,599
