734
00:28:34,599 --> 00:28:35,079
Mom.

735
00:28:35,839 --> 00:28:37,319
We really didn't win the lottery?

736
00:28:37,400 --> 00:28:38,319
No.

737
00:28:38,799 --> 00:28:39,599
When did I ever say

738
00:28:39,599 --> 00:28:40,759
