744
00:28:47,519 --> 00:28:48,319
So what?

745
00:28:48,480 --> 00:28:49,599
As long as your heart is at ease.

746
00:28:49,880 --> 00:28:50,359
Right?

747
00:28:50,759 --> 00:28:51,680
Young body,

748
00:28:52,279 --> 00:28:53,440
