751
00:29:03,839 --> 00:29:04,319
Hello?

752
00:29:04,799 --> 00:29:05,319
Ms. Wang.

753
00:29:05,480 --> 00:29:06,359
Yitong.

754
00:29:06,480 --> 00:29:07,640
Some of my girlfriends

755
00:29:07,640 --> 00:29:08,640
