756
00:29:08,799 --> 00:29:09,960
Set something up for me.

757
00:29:09,960 --> 00:29:11,039
Well, I...

758
00:29:11,119 --> 00:29:11,799
I'm not

759
00:29:11,799 --> 00:29:13,079
