760
00:29:13,319 --> 00:29:14,000
I quit.

761
00:29:14,839 --> 00:29:16,440
Why would you quit?

762
00:29:16,519 --> 00:29:17,400
I came this time

763
00:29:17,400 --> 00:29:18,680
because of you.

764
00:29:19,400 --> 00:29:21,279
We are in the same circle now.

765
00:29:21,359 --> 00:29:21,759
How about this?

766
00:29:21,759 --> 00:29:22,680
I can recommend

767
00:29:22,880 --> 00:29:23,920
another travel agency.

768
00:29:23,920 --> 00:29:24,920
A friend of mine works there.

769
00:29:25,039 --> 00:29:26,160
They do great work too.

770
00:29:27,279 --> 00:29:28,480
I will send you his contact now.

771
00:29:37,119 --> 00:29:38,039
Please have a seat.

772
00:29:38,119 --> 00:29:38,720
I will be right back.

773
00:29:40,200 --> 00:29:40,640
Hey.

774
00:29:41,920 --> 00:29:43,079
Are you two on a date?

775
00:29:43,279 --> 00:29:43,839
Yes.

776
00:29:48,240 --> 00:29:49,000
One more.

777
00:29:49,039 --> 00:29:49,559
Tequila.

778
00:29:52,119 --> 00:29:52,960
Make hers special.

779
00:29:55,200 --> 00:29:57,279
Shiqi. You are terrible.

780
00:29:57,640 --> 00:29:58,839
Got her this drunk.

781
00:29:59,119 --> 00:29:59,960
I did not order them.

782
00:29:59,960 --> 00:30:00,799
She did.

783
00:30:01,000 --> 00:30:02,160
I told the bartender,

784
00:30:02,200 --> 00:30:03,359
after five drinks, no alcohol.

785
00:30:03,359 --> 00:30:04,160
She can't tell.

786
00:30:06,480 --> 00:30:07,279
You here for a party?

787
00:30:08,240 --> 00:30:10,480
Yes. An online mixer.

788
00:30:11,720 --> 00:30:12,200
See that guy

789
00:30:12,200 --> 00:30:13,240
