790
00:30:16,599 --> 00:30:17,480
My new target.

791
00:30:19,119 --> 00:30:20,200
You moved on fast.

792
00:30:20,200 --> 00:30:21,160
Didn't you just break up?

793
00:30:22,440 --> 00:30:24,359
I don't like dragging things out.

794
00:30:24,680 --> 00:30:25,880
It makes me feel

795
00:30:25,880 --> 00:30:27,799
I was never truly chosen.

796
00:30:28,599 --> 00:30:30,960
If you love someone, be brave.

797
00:30:32,039 --> 00:30:33,200
Miss the right moment,

798
00:30:33,559 --> 00:30:35,160
and you may lose the chance.

799
00:30:39,000 --> 00:30:39,759
Are you talking about me?

800
00:30:40,279 --> 00:30:40,839
Who else?

801
00:30:42,960 --> 00:30:43,480
Ouyang Qing.

802
00:30:43,880 --> 00:30:44,440
Come join us.

803
00:30:45,119 --> 00:30:45,640
Coming.

804
00:30:46,559 --> 00:30:47,359
Want to come?

805
00:30:47,759 --> 00:30:48,720
No. I'm too old for this.

806
00:30:51,200 --> 00:30:51,640
Fine.

807
00:30:52,079 --> 00:30:52,640
I will leave you two

808
00:30:52,640 --> 00:30:53,480
to your little date.

809
00:30:53,920 --> 00:30:54,519
Good luck.

810
00:31:06,240 --> 00:31:07,599
Isn't this taking advantage of regulars?

811
00:31:08,240 --> 00:31:09,680
She used to work so hard.

812
00:31:09,720 --> 00:31:10,880
I liked hearing her talk

813
00:31:10,880 --> 00:31:11,960
about the history of the sights.

814
00:31:12,079 --> 00:31:13,440
She knew her facts,

815
00:31:13,440 --> 00:31:14,880
and she made them come alive.

816
00:31:15,039 --> 00:31:15,680
Now?

817
00:31:15,759 --> 00:31:17,440
She follows that tacky rich man

818
00:31:17,480 --> 00:31:18,519
with a bag of cash,

819
00:31:18,559 --> 00:31:19,359
showing off everywhere.

820
00:31:19,359 --> 00:31:20,960
