821
00:31:21,400 --> 00:31:21,880
Please.

822
00:31:22,279 --> 00:31:23,240
130 million?

823
00:31:23,319 --> 00:31:24,759
What a joke!

824
00:31:25,039 --> 00:31:25,519
Well,

825
00:31:25,680 --> 00:31:26,519
