826
00:31:26,599 --> 00:31:27,640
Where is her honesty?

827
00:31:27,640 --> 00:31:29,160
Her professionalism?

828
00:31:29,720 --> 00:31:31,279
About her taking commissions outside,

829
00:31:31,279 --> 00:31:31,920
