830
00:31:32,079 --> 00:31:32,880
What commissions?

831
00:31:32,880 --> 00:31:33,880
Did she take you shopping?

832
00:31:34,079 --> 00:31:34,839
No, no.

833
00:31:34,839 --> 00:31:36,359
As if I would buy it.

834
00:31:36,400 --> 00:31:36,880
She sent me

835
00:31:36,880 --> 00:31:37,799
to another travel agency.

836
00:31:37,799 --> 00:31:38,480
Wait.

837
00:31:39,839 --> 00:31:40,440
Ms. Wang.

838
00:31:41,240 --> 00:31:42,200
She sent you

839
00:31:42,200 --> 00:31:43,279
to another agency?

840
00:31:43,559 --> 00:31:44,319
Exactly.

841
00:31:44,319 --> 00:31:45,160
Do you know what kind of car

842
00:31:45,160 --> 00:31:46,359
