843
00:31:46,960 --> 00:31:47,880
A minibus.

844
00:31:48,039 --> 00:31:49,279
What am I, cargo?

845
00:31:49,440 --> 00:31:50,759
I was crammed in there,

846
00:31:50,839 --> 00:31:52,000
