847
00:31:52,000 --> 00:31:53,079
I looked like a rose apple.

848
00:31:53,079 --> 00:31:53,680
The whole trip

849
00:31:53,799 --> 00:31:55,079
was a complete mess.

850
00:31:55,599 --> 00:31:57,279
You are still the best.

851
00:31:57,440 --> 00:31:58,839
You would never treat me like that.

852
00:31:59,799 --> 00:32:00,359
Would you?

853
00:32:01,279 --> 00:32:01,759
Never.

854
00:32:01,960 --> 00:32:02,920
Never, Ms. Wang.

855
00:32:03,319 --> 00:32:05,799
You are our super VIP,

856
00:32:05,799 --> 00:32:06,880
our top-tier client.

857
00:32:07,000 --> 00:32:07,799
When you five elegant ladies

858
00:32:07,799 --> 00:32:08,599
travel with us,

859
00:32:08,599 --> 00:32:10,279
you get luxury business transport,

860
00:32:10,279 --> 00:32:11,240
food and drinks included,

861
00:32:11,279 --> 00:32:12,759
full VIP treatment.

862
00:32:12,799 --> 00:32:13,480
Put it this way.

863
00:32:13,680 --> 00:32:14,920
If you wanted to go to the moon,

864
00:32:14,960 --> 00:32:15,519
I would

865
00:32:15,559 --> 00:32:16,640
bring you a ladder

866
00:32:16,640 --> 00:32:17,400
right away.

867
00:32:17,680 --> 00:32:19,160
That is why I trust you.

868
00:32:19,240 --> 00:32:19,720
As for her,

869
00:32:19,960 --> 00:32:21,799
