873
00:32:40,500 --> 00:32:42,330
(Employment Contract, Wen Yitong)

874
00:32:42,799 --> 00:32:44,319
Way to go, Wen Yitong.

875
00:32:44,480 --> 00:32:45,359
You actually introduced Ms. Wang

876
00:32:45,359 --> 00:32:46,680
