887
00:33:24,480 --> 00:33:25,079
Please, come in.

888
00:33:25,319 --> 00:33:26,119
No, no.

889
00:33:26,240 --> 00:33:26,960
I...

890
00:33:27,400 --> 00:33:28,640
I'm looking for this shade of lipstick.

891
00:33:33,400 --> 00:33:34,839
Ma'am, this is...

892
00:33:34,880 --> 00:33:35,519
I lived with Song Youcheng

893
00:33:35,519 --> 00:33:36,480
for sixteen years.

894
00:33:36,640 --> 00:33:37,400
I never had

895
00:33:37,400 --> 00:33:38,279
a single good day.

896
00:33:38,319 --> 00:33:39,119
When we first got wealthy,

897
00:33:39,160 --> 00:33:40,039
- I was managing the household.
- Madam.

898
00:33:40,160 --> 00:33:40,920
Give me this first.

899
00:33:40,920 --> 00:33:42,039
He said we had to go big for New Year,

900
00:33:42,319 --> 00:33:42,960
or we'd lose face.

901
00:33:42,960 --> 00:33:44,119
I had no choice, trying to save money,

902
00:33:44,240 --> 00:33:45,519
I even made the sausages myself.

903
00:33:45,759 --> 00:33:46,480
I stood in the kitchen

904
00:33:46,759 --> 00:33:47,880
wearing an apron all day.

905
00:33:47,880 --> 00:33:49,240
I had to cut the meat and season it.

906
00:33:49,279 --> 00:33:50,039
My arms were so tired

907
00:33:50,039 --> 00:33:50,400
that I couldn't lift them.

908
00:33:50,400 --> 00:33:50,880
You go ahead.

909
00:33:51,400 --> 00:33:51,960
Youcheng.

910
00:33:53,079 --> 00:33:53,720
Why are you here?

911
00:33:53,839 --> 00:33:54,759
Let's talk at home. Come on.

912
00:33:54,839 --> 00:33:55,960
Even the kids looked down on me.

913
00:33:56,039 --> 00:33:56,759
Now that things are better,

914
00:33:56,759 --> 00:33:57,559
- Let's talk at home.
- I wanted

915
00:33:57,640 --> 00:33:58,440
to do something I enjoy.

916
00:33:58,440 --> 00:33:59,440
But you wouldn't let me.

917
00:33:59,680 --> 00:34:00,400
I just want to ask,

918
00:34:00,519 --> 00:34:01,920
whose lipstick is this?

919
00:34:02,039 --> 00:34:02,599
Stop it!

920
00:34:02,599 --> 00:34:03,599
Who is the woman wearing this lipstick?

921
00:34:03,640 --> 00:34:04,880
Can she make sausages?

922
00:34:04,960 --> 00:34:05,759
Can she?

923
00:34:06,039 --> 00:34:07,160
Let go of me!

924
00:34:07,240 --> 00:34:08,039
Stop it!

925
00:34:08,039 --> 00:34:08,920
- Get lost!
- No!

926
00:34:09,079 --> 00:34:10,199
- I want to see who it is!
- Come on!

927
00:34:10,199 --> 00:34:11,280
Who is the woman with this lipstick?

928
00:34:11,280 --> 00:34:12,400
Can she make sausages?

929
00:34:12,480 --> 00:34:13,440
Let me go!

930
00:34:13,480 --> 00:34:14,880
Stop watching.

931
00:34:15,280 --> 00:34:15,960
Back to work!

932
00:34:16,400 --> 00:34:17,719
Can she make sausages?

933
00:34:18,000 --> 00:34:18,599
Xinlu.

934
00:34:18,760 --> 00:34:19,239
Sit down.

935
00:34:19,559 --> 00:34:20,199
Let go of me!

936
00:34:20,639 --> 00:34:21,800
You're just scared I'll find out!

937
00:34:22,119 --> 00:34:23,079
Let go of me!

938
00:34:23,159 --> 00:34:24,679
I need to know who that woman is.

939
00:34:24,960 --> 00:34:26,159
Can you stop this?

940
00:34:26,159 --> 00:34:27,000
Let go of me!

941
00:34:27,039 --> 00:34:27,599
Go!

942
00:34:27,719 --> 00:34:28,280
Get up!

943
00:34:28,800 --> 00:34:29,199
Leave!

944
00:34:29,960 --> 00:34:30,880
Can she?

945
00:34:31,320 --> 00:34:32,320
- Let go of me!
- You're crazy!

946
00:34:32,920 --> 00:34:33,880
Let go!

947
00:34:35,559 --> 00:34:36,320
Let go of me!

948
00:34:36,320 --> 00:34:37,360
Can you stop this?

949
00:34:37,360 --> 00:34:38,119
I'm not leaving!

950
00:34:38,599 --> 00:34:39,199
Go!

951
00:34:39,280 --> 00:34:39,719
Go!

952
00:34:39,920 --> 00:34:40,920
Don't make me lose my temper.

953
00:34:41,760 --> 00:34:42,760
- I'm not leaving.
- Go!

954
00:34:43,079 --> 00:34:44,239
I have to know who she is!

955
00:34:44,320 --> 00:34:44,920
Who is she?

956
00:34:44,920 --> 00:34:45,679
Let go. Let go!

957
00:34:45,760 --> 00:34:46,639
Hey!

958
00:34:47,119 --> 00:34:48,400
Why do you meddle in everything?

959
00:34:48,639 --> 00:34:49,400
Are you bored or something?

960
00:34:49,599 --> 00:34:50,360
She is my wife.

961
00:34:50,360 --> 00:34:51,239
So what?

962
00:34:51,239 --> 00:34:52,400
Domestic violence is illegal.

963
00:34:52,440 --> 00:34:53,440
Look at you.

964
00:34:53,440 --> 00:34:54,440
Only tough at home.

965
00:34:54,480 --> 00:34:55,239
Illegal?

966
00:34:55,840 --> 00:34:57,000
Fine. Fine.

967
00:34:57,639 --> 00:34:58,639
Let us talk law.

968
00:34:59,159 --> 00:35:00,639
What about your breach of contract?

969
00:35:02,840 --> 00:35:03,559
Check it out.

970
00:35:03,610 --> 00:35:04,990
(Employment Contract)

971
00:35:06,960 --> 00:35:07,480
I don't need to.

972
00:35:07,480 --> 00:35:08,719
Let me give you a quick law lesson.

973
00:35:10,159 --> 00:35:11,679
A non-compete clause

974
00:35:11,679 --> 00:35:13,599
has clear legal limits.

975
00:35:13,679 --> 00:35:14,920
It applies to

976
00:35:14,920 --> 00:35:16,079
senior technical staff

977
00:35:16,079 --> 00:35:17,559
or senior management.

978
00:35:17,559 --> 00:35:18,239
And what am I?

979
00:35:18,280 --> 00:35:19,440
A low-level team leader

980
00:35:19,440 --> 00:35:20,639
at your little company.

981
00:35:20,719 --> 00:35:22,000
You never promoted me,

982
00:35:22,000 --> 00:35:22,480
did you?

983
00:35:23,159 --> 00:35:23,760
Well,

984
00:35:24,039 --> 00:35:24,599
do not stand here

985
00:35:24,599 --> 00:35:25,760
twisting words with me.

986
00:35:26,840 --> 00:35:27,480
Is that clause

987
00:35:27,480 --> 00:35:28,360
in the contract or not?

988
00:35:29,760 --> 00:35:30,840
Isn't that your signature?

989
00:35:31,599 --> 00:35:32,920
Once you sign a contract,

990
00:35:33,199 --> 00:35:34,039
it is binding.

991
00:35:34,920 --> 00:35:35,679
Break it,

992
00:35:36,199 --> 00:35:37,119
and you face a lawsuit.

993
00:35:38,519 --> 00:35:39,760
You really are clueless.

994
00:35:39,920 --> 00:35:40,559
You know nothing,

995
00:35:40,559 --> 00:35:41,880
yet you keep threatening lawsuits.

996
00:35:41,960 --> 00:35:43,000
Are you trying to shake me down?

997
00:35:43,039 --> 00:35:43,760
If this is about money,

998
00:35:43,760 --> 00:35:44,840
let us talk money.

999
00:35:45,119 --> 00:35:46,119
Since I started here,

1000
00:35:46,159 --> 00:35:47,480
have I ever received

1001
00:35:47,480 --> 00:35:48,960
any non-compete compensation?

1002
00:35:49,079 --> 00:35:50,559
I run this company.

1003
00:35:50,559 --> 00:35:51,400
Run it all you want.

1004
00:35:51,400 --> 00:35:52,559
I never received a cent.

1005
00:35:52,559 --> 00:35:53,920
Then it has no legal force.

1006
00:35:53,920 --> 00:35:54,480
Understand?

1007
00:35:55,679 --> 00:35:56,440
Go ahead and sue me.

1008
00:35:56,440 --> 00:35:57,400
Take this with you.

1009
00:35:57,559 --> 00:35:58,480
You don't know a thing.

1010
00:35:58,480 --> 00:36:00,079
Buy some law books sometime.

1011
00:36:00,079 --> 00:36:01,039
Put them on that shelf.

1012
00:36:01,119 --> 00:36:01,920
Even flipping a bit would help.

1013
00:36:02,199 --> 00:36:03,039
You never do anything decent.

1014
00:36:03,039 --> 00:36:04,519
Only know how to play with turtles.

1015
00:36:04,519 --> 00:36:05,559
Unbelievable.

1016
00:36:08,639 --> 00:36:09,239
Where is she?

1017
00:36:09,800 --> 00:36:10,400
Tong.

1018
00:36:35,199 --> 00:36:36,280
That lipstick mark was mine.

1019
00:36:37,239 --> 00:36:37,760
Yes.

1020
00:36:38,360 --> 00:36:39,360
I use whatever means I have to.

1021
00:36:39,840 --> 00:36:40,760
I care about profit.

1022
00:36:41,039 --> 00:36:42,119
I want a better life,

1023
00:36:42,159 --> 00:36:42,840
then an even better one.

1024
00:36:43,039 --> 00:36:43,599
So what?

1025
00:36:45,599 --> 00:36:46,719
Nothing. Fair enough.

1026
00:36:47,039 --> 00:36:48,360
I know you all dislike me.

1027
00:36:49,000 --> 00:36:49,679
But it's fine.

1028
00:36:49,920 --> 00:36:51,599
So what if we find you annoying?

1029
00:36:52,119 --> 00:36:53,239
Most of the time,

1030
00:36:53,280 --> 00:36:54,119
you annoy me.

1031
00:36:54,280 --> 00:36:55,719
But you still do whatever you want.

1032
00:36:55,880 --> 00:36:56,679
This is who I am now.

1033
00:36:57,400 --> 00:36:58,119
So let it be.

1034
00:36:58,199 --> 00:36:59,079
Is it really?

1035
00:37:06,079 --> 00:37:06,719
What do you mean?

1036
00:37:06,719 --> 00:37:07,519
You were not like this.

1037
00:37:07,960 --> 00:37:09,239
On your first day at the company,

1038
00:37:09,239 --> 00:37:10,039
you wore a white shirt

1039
00:37:10,039 --> 00:37:10,840
and a high ponytail.

1040
00:37:11,079 --> 00:37:12,039
You checked in at reception.

1041
00:37:12,280 --> 00:37:12,960
Then you turned around,

1042
00:37:13,239 --> 00:37:14,159
said hello to me,

1043
00:37:14,199 --> 00:37:15,039
and smiled so wide.

1044
00:37:15,239 --> 00:37:15,840
Right then, I thought,

1045
00:37:15,840 --> 00:37:17,360
this girl is real. She is good.

1046
00:37:19,000 --> 00:37:20,199
When I took you on your first one,

1047
00:37:20,320 --> 00:37:21,519
you worked through the itinerary

1048
00:37:21,519 --> 00:37:22,360
all night.

1049
00:37:22,599 --> 00:37:23,239
It was almost morning.

1050
00:37:23,239 --> 00:37:24,320
You were half-asleep.

1051
00:37:24,559 --> 00:37:25,679
Then you said to me,

1052
00:37:26,159 --> 00:37:27,119
"This route is wonderful.

1053
00:37:27,159 --> 00:37:29,000
I wish I could take my mom there."

1054
00:37:29,239 --> 00:37:30,079
That was the moment

1055
00:37:30,599 --> 00:37:32,159
I decided to bring you in.

1056
00:37:34,920 --> 00:37:35,800
In this life,

1057
00:37:35,800 --> 00:37:37,159
you can be whoever you want

1058
00:37:37,159 --> 00:37:38,880
and live however you choose.

1059
00:37:39,159 --> 00:37:40,400
That is your choice.

1060
00:37:40,440 --> 00:37:41,920
You don't need anyone's approval.

1061
00:37:42,079 --> 00:37:42,679
It does not matter.

1062
00:37:43,119 --> 00:37:44,719
But your heart and actions should match.

1063
00:37:45,159 --> 00:37:46,760
Who you are deep down

1064
00:37:46,800 --> 00:37:47,800
and who you show

1065
00:37:47,800 --> 00:37:48,519
to the world now

1066
00:37:48,519 --> 00:37:49,679
should be the same.

1067
00:37:49,800 --> 00:37:50,760
Otherwise, you suffer,

1068
00:37:50,760 --> 00:37:51,880
and so does everyone else.

1069
00:37:58,960 --> 00:38:00,440
Anyway, I've left the company.

1070
00:38:01,920 --> 00:38:02,719
For the rest of our lives,

1071
00:38:02,719 --> 00:38:04,239
we probably won't cross paths much.

1072
00:38:05,719 --> 00:38:06,559
Before I go,

1073
00:38:06,559 --> 00:38:07,880
I just want to tell you something.

1074
00:38:08,280 --> 00:38:08,840
Don't forget

1075
00:38:08,840 --> 00:38:10,119
the kind of person you once were.

1076
00:38:11,960 --> 00:38:12,719
You won't forget.

1077
00:39:03,000 --> 00:39:03,880
Hurry and put it on.

1078
00:39:08,519 --> 00:39:09,119
Not bad.

1079
00:39:10,840 --> 00:39:11,360
Remember,

1080
00:39:12,440 --> 00:39:13,480
these are

1081
00:39:13,480 --> 00:39:14,960
our company's VIP clients.

1082
00:39:15,320 --> 00:39:18,039
These are cash-rich clients.

1083
00:39:19,519 --> 00:39:20,199
Make sure you

1084
00:39:20,199 --> 00:39:21,440
take good care of them.

1085
00:39:22,000 --> 00:39:23,159
Show off your skills.

1086
00:39:23,480 --> 00:39:26,280
Be a little sexy and charming.

1087
00:39:30,760 --> 00:39:32,320
No deadpan face.

1088
00:39:33,320 --> 00:39:34,519
This isn't a funeral home.

1089
00:39:36,760 --> 00:39:37,639
Smile.

1090
00:40:34,652 --> 00:40:35,443
(Jiari International Travel Agency)

1091
00:40:40,679 --> 00:40:41,400
Xinlu.

1092
00:40:53,920 --> 00:40:54,440
What's up?

1093
00:40:54,639 --> 00:40:56,760
Taxpayers falsify or alter,

1094
00:40:56,920 --> 00:40:58,880
hide or destroy accounting documents,

1095
00:40:58,960 --> 00:41:00,280
underreport or omit income,

1096
00:41:00,480 --> 00:41:02,679
fail to pay or underpay taxes,

1097
00:41:02,679 --> 00:41:04,280
all of which constitute tax evasion.

1098
00:41:04,280 --> 00:41:05,719
The actions carry legal consequences.

1099
00:41:18,239 --> 00:41:19,119
Where did you get all this?

1100
00:41:19,320 --> 00:41:20,440
You didn't even try to stop me.

1101
00:41:21,199 --> 00:41:22,840
It's not like it's hard to get these.

1102
00:41:23,159 --> 00:41:23,920
Is that surprising?

1103
00:41:28,239 --> 00:41:29,719
If I can print one copy,

1104
00:41:29,960 --> 00:41:31,400
I can print 100.

1105
00:41:31,880 --> 00:41:32,840
And that's not all.

1106
00:41:33,280 --> 00:41:34,039
Violations,

1107
00:41:34,440 --> 00:41:35,199
misappropriations.

1108
00:41:36,079 --> 00:41:38,119
If all this got out,

1109
00:41:38,119 --> 00:41:39,079
what would happen to you?

1110
00:41:39,880 --> 00:41:40,440
Have you thought about it?

1111
00:41:45,480 --> 00:41:46,800
What exactly do you want?

1112
00:41:52,519 --> 00:41:54,320
Stay away from Ms. Wen.

1113
00:41:54,840 --> 00:41:56,559
Stop causing trouble for her.

1114
00:41:57,239 --> 00:41:58,079
Otherwise,

1115
00:41:58,639 --> 00:42:00,000
I will hand all this

1116
00:42:00,239 --> 00:42:01,599
over to the authorities.

1117
00:42:06,320 --> 00:42:06,840
Goodbye.

1118
00:42:08,079 --> 00:42:08,519
Wait.

1119
00:42:09,000 --> 00:42:09,920
Better yet,

1120
00:42:10,840 --> 00:42:12,039
let's never meet again.

1121
00:42:18,639 --> 00:42:19,760
Ms. Wen is right.

1122
00:42:22,320 --> 00:42:23,599
You're a coward, like this turtle.

1123
00:42:43,960 --> 00:42:45,599
♪Work hard and make money♪

1124
00:42:45,800 --> 00:42:47,079
♪I want to get rich♪

1125
00:42:47,559 --> 00:42:49,320
♪A villa by the sea♪

1126
00:42:51,519 --> 00:42:52,039
Hello?

1127
00:42:52,719 --> 00:42:53,480
I'm Li Jin.

1128
00:42:54,719 --> 00:42:55,880
Chen Zinuo's mother.

1129
00:42:57,360 --> 00:42:58,920
You have the money from Unit 505, right?

1130
00:42:59,719 --> 00:43:00,840
We should talk in person.

1131
00:43:05,080 --> 00:43:07,880
(Next Episode)

1132
00:43:08,280 --> 00:43:09,639
(Actor, Guo Jingfei)
Hi, I'm Guo Jingfei.

1133
00:43:09,639 --> 00:43:11,960
(Actor, Guo Jingfei)
I invite you to watch Wonder Wall.

1134
00:43:12,440 --> 00:43:12,920
That's her.

1135
00:43:13,199 --> 00:43:14,519
Got a plan to deal with her?

1136
00:43:15,440 --> 00:43:16,119
Just don't give it back.

1137
00:43:16,280 --> 00:43:17,199
A hundred thousand,

1138
00:43:17,400 --> 00:43:18,199
a few hundred thousand,

1139
00:43:18,320 --> 00:43:20,119
they can all cause a huge uproar,

1140
00:43:20,159 --> 00:43:21,400
So what do you think

1141
00:43:21,400 --> 00:43:22,119
30 million would do?

1142
00:43:23,760 --> 00:43:25,199
Another 30 million?

1143
00:43:26,000 --> 00:43:27,119
Can you listen to me for once?

1144
00:43:27,159 --> 00:43:27,880
Now things have

1145
00:43:27,880 --> 00:43:29,039
gotten out of control.

1146
00:43:29,039 --> 00:43:29,559
You know that.

1147
00:43:32,559 --> 00:43:33,480
Oh, my god!

1148
00:43:33,599 --> 00:43:35,320
What happened to you?

1149
00:43:35,679 --> 00:43:36,639
Did he beat you again?

1150
00:43:36,639 --> 00:43:37,760
No.

1151
00:43:55,610 --> 00:44:02,620
♪The road ahead is still so long
Where have you gone?♪

1152
00:44:04,180 --> 00:44:11,340
♪Under the blazing sun
I keep heading north♪

1153
00:44:12,760 --> 00:44:20,220
♪To those who pass me by
You don't have to look at me♪

1154
00:44:21,360 --> 00:44:28,640
♪Just keep walking your own way
I'll manage on my own♪

1155
00:44:31,630 --> 00:44:35,230
♪Is the rain falling hard?♪

1156
00:44:35,870 --> 00:44:39,000
♪Is there someone
to hold an umbrella for you?♪

1157
00:44:40,160 --> 00:44:44,940
♪The wind has blown
the numbers off the signs♪

1158
00:44:44,940 --> 00:44:47,930
♪Where am I supposed to go?♪

1159
00:44:48,730 --> 00:44:52,250
♪Can I change my mind?♪

1160
00:44:53,010 --> 00:44:56,240
♪How do I go on without you?♪

1161
00:44:57,550 --> 00:45:02,080
♪When will this
endless rain finally stop?♪

1162
00:45:02,080 --> 00:45:04,780
♪Then I'll wait for you♪

1163
00:45:04,780 --> 00:45:08,780
♪Please don't leave me waiting♪

